title: Nick Holt - The Mammoth Book of the World Cup (2014).
description:
The Mammoth Book of the World Cup,

by Nick Holt.

  
# ISBN-13: 9780762452248 
# Publisher: Running Press Book Publishers
# Publication date: 5/6/2014
# Pages: 784


A guide to the one of the few truly international events. It covers everything from its roots in Uruguay in 1930 to the modern all-singing, all-dancing Greatest Show on Earth!

Author
======

Nick Holt has written a number of books on sport, music, film, and other aspects of popular culture.
